OL,6,FA number of homes and a school in
OL,7,FMerthyr Tydfil are still experiencing
OL,8,Fissues with their water supply after a
OL,9,Fburst water pipe led to people's homes
OL,10,Fbeing flooded.
OL,12,FResidents in Trelewis, Merthyr Tydfil,
OL,13,Fhad been worst affected by the
OL,14,Fflooding on Wednesday, with Trelewis
OL,15,FCommunity Centre offering shelter for
OL,16,Fthose affected.
