OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil County Borough Council
OL,7,Fposted on X, formerly Twitter, on
OL,8,FThursday morning saying: "We are aware
OL,9,Fthat some areas in Merthyr Tydfil are
OL,10,Fstill experiencing issues due to the
OL,11,Fburst water pipe incident that took
OL,12,Fplace yesterday in Trelewis."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Dwr Cymru Welsh Water
OL,15,Fposted an update on X: "We've worked
OL,16,Fovernight to replace the damaged water
OL,17,Fmain.
